description: Mitsubishi sat out the 2003 WRC season to develop a radical rethink of their Lancer Evolution WRC. The WRC04 had over 6000 changes done over the WRC02 with a redesigned AWD system and a radical aero package developed at Lola Cars' wind tunnel. Despite all those changes, Mitsubishi had a tough start to the 2004 WRC season and did not finish the season, opting to develop the car further.
creator: Bnuuy
